      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Medium close-up of a man in a suit.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Nikola Angelov Zahariev (1898 - 1945) was a Bulgarian politician, deputy, Minister of Railway, Postal- and Telegraphic Services (1934 - 1935) as well as Minister of Trade, Industry and Labour (1942 - 1943). He was sentenced to death by a "People's Tribunal" (Naroden sad) in 1945 and executed. He was rehabilitated 1996.</ab>
